OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, Tuesday
OL,6,Fwill be dry with plenty of sunny
OL,7,Fspells. The wind will become light and
OL,8,Fvariable but remaining breezy along
OL,9,Fthe coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FOvernight under clear skies
OL,12,Fthe temperature will fall close to
OL,13,Ffreezing with frost patches possible.
OL,14,FThe light winds could also give rise
OL,15,Fto some fog patches forming.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FPatchy cloud and sunny
OL,18,Fspells expected, light winds continue
OL,19,Fbut breezy along the coast. Fog and
OL,20,Flow cloud developing Wednesday night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
